barbie in the 12 dancing princesses is a direct-to-video computer animated barbie film directed by greg richardson and loosely based on the fairytale " the twelve dancing princesses " .   it is part of the barbie film series and features the voice of kelly sheridan as barbie .   this film was released on february 21 , 2006 .   music for the film was composed by arnie roth .   " shine " , the end title song written by roth , amy powers and rob hudnut , was nominated for a 2007 emmy award .